{"tid":1829744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毋忘初衷] 一人n個你會開始做黃絲嘅原因","createTime":"2020-01-19T04:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:34:14.000Z","uid":299134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"01351e20491cf91f64045dace52212e1d9f5a234","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"如果你重未決定好今日去唔去中環，歡迎你入嚟睇下呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再諗返起自己嘅初衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由上年6月到宜家，呢場社會運動已經持續咗7個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係多得大家嘅努力，場運動先可以維持到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而你又記唔記得，自己點解當初會決定做一個黃絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎喺度同大家分享下自己係因為咩原因而開始做黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重覆都唔緊要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">記得唔好透露夢境細節！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n喺6.9嘅時候，知道有100萬人上街遊行反對逃犯條例嘅修訂，覺得好震驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但換嚟嘅只係政府宣布二讀如期舉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到咗6.12，見到香港人好努力咁去阻止恢復二讀修例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而喺嗰日，啲黑警竟然用槍去射人哋頭部，喺未有警告之下開槍射中一位教師嘅右眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係明明有守則講明開槍只可以射下肢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺有申請不反對通知書嘅和平集會區，放tg幾面夾擊啲示威者，迫啲人湧入中信，向人群中央扔tg迫佢哋硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，重要差啲造成人踩人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到都覺得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後換嚟嘅只係正苦宣布暫緩修例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺6.15下晝，上連登嘅時候見到有post講，有位着住黃色雨褸嘅巴打喺太古廣場企跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢企喺廣場外面嘅臨時工作平台，喺嗰度掛上反送中橫額，於是一直喺度追post，揾下有冇其他新聞source，睇下有冇最新消息，好擔心佢嘅安危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺嗰日夜晚，當消防想捉住爬出棚架嘅佢，想救佢嘅時候，結果都係捉唔住佢，跌咗落行人路上面⋯⋯就係咁睇住位巴打，由企跳，到捉唔住，跌咗落嚟，上咗白車送院，最後做咗烈士⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />眼白白睇住咁失去手足，而自己點解乜嘢都做唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個極權正苦同濫暴嘅黑警，就係咁迫死咗珍貴嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(諗返起呢件事，打緊呢段嘅時候，心酸咗一下，突然之間眼濕濕，想喊出嚟又驚比其他人聽到⋯⋯心情難以形容)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見住香港發生咗啲咁嘅事，令一直少關心時事嘅自己從「自由繁榮安定嘅香港」嘅夢境中醒返，原來自己一直喺温水入面，畀人煮緊都唔知⋯⋯咁自己要繼續扮瞓，定係開始為自己發聲，企出嚟抵抗呢個極權正苦？相信已經有咗答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後發生更多嘅遊行示威被打壓，一連串嘅黑警濫暴濫捕事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，選擇性執法，香港人被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，極權正苦縱容，漠視民意，硬推惡法，香港法治已成笑話，我哋應有嘅自由都消失咗⋯⋯港共正苦數之不盡嘅惡行，令自己更肯定要企出嚟反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有721 811 831 101 113 1111<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我永遠都唔會忘記呢啲日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以麻目<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌少出post講嘢可能有啲1999，請大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後補多句：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x51OO6U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx51OO6U.gif&h=1a6c494a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人面對極權都唔會退縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當初企出嚟嘅初衷係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日，你又會唔會企出嚟，堅持落去，齊上齊落呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n你若放棄 誰衛我城？<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"eda91dabb38e3f482f4ae917ba6a62bbd3789bc5","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"港共受刑 天下制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFjwP4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFjwP4F.jpg&h=6a3c1db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ade3077f2a1bed87f12fc1d85f14e5c43aa48e48","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84dc4622411816fa8c5c2a1ea2b18b5af393a5c","tid":1829744,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"上連登"},{"pid":"56351f3a832991761245c255e9134989d90e52f5","tid":1829744,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:47:31.000Z","msg":"雨革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1216f6126c45df00c35d30239c7b4211aa809b","tid":1829744,"uid":282098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"中學讀雙史"},{"pid":"ad65d1924df7152d8db5bc111c8442773a4cd370","tid":1829744,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"唔想真係見到有人敵中"},{"pid":"5e3f30d596e5838904be559d84ea7fd85327667c","tid":1829744,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"仲有樓主你發夢啲故仔擺上講故台"},{"pid":"b413785650b11c9672b58e78f18591239a12692f","tid":1829744,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c29667cb8e8aefba616db38d81bc1aaf0dc128d","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hc5TiY8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHc5TiY8.gif&h=1c73152a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nP推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a155f741537e07d2e185e9dfe5764c1ffc196da","tid":1829744,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:49:38.000Z","msg":"反高鐵撥款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007a3c14aae060ec87f3b31f79a6b615ccdb16b1","tid":1829744,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"雨革開始"},{"pid":"78026a6db4f7c990be70f9d4a7ef41222b5a54f6","tid":1829744,"uid":146520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"因為有阿媽生，自然會係黃"},{"pid":"7eba9343944703a471be12d214b284ddce115b08","tid":1829744,"uid":141095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"信奉民主 自由 公義<br />\n希望可以保護下一代仲有以上嘅嘢"},{"pid":"b54efa545fa169d7d13dea847903298594dca75c","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"P推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毋忘初衷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb94b5f31a70a7aaa34aca6e77d88d19138be8c","tid":1829744,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b333765a9255f9c273164782661c15cf0106f9c","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"P推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTnyi2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTnyi2U.gif&h=c6e65bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oD1K99C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoD1K99C.png&h=44dd8291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e393f806df9ee78303171c718040ab52911cf43","tid":1829744,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"928睇直播第一次見到催淚彈<br />\nd人行哂出馬路"},{"pid":"f111a528744f623f912cffc77fabfd8d3deae3da","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"P推5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zg04qJv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZg04qJv.gif&h=0e420922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqp5aaa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcqp5aaa.gif&h=bfb90645&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cf84d8dadd6a64b6f3114a0620046215027d764","tid":1829744,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"P推6<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nuQv5JO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnuQv5JO.gif&h=5863bed9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEU8SoP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEU8SoP.gif&h=c770357c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d7fbc3f99af94a276906b9254cb55ff465772df","tid":1829744,"uid":38391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"反國教"},{"pid":"9721e6c1fc749a5920f515bf2bc5f749519535b7","tid":1829744,"uid":179963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"也試過制度和自由"},{"pid":"0c08c419ca418500af8b2494279153b8fb87d7dd","tid":1829744,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1DBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=dd8c36cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n<br />\n另外, 所羅門聯署:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1DBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=0c8d05f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a>"},{"pid":"d304cd5d34f3dc484ae83081ece56b3e762fae26","tid":1829744,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"雨傘淺黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec7c4a6d403e6bb1a9fc68394827c94bff9cadb","tid":1829744,"uid":208568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"良知"}]}